                <title xml:lang="en">On the Prodigal Son.</title>
                
                
                
                
                
                <note>See <bibl>Opera, t. viii., p. 656</bibl>, from <foreign xml:lang="grc">Καὶ τοῦτο δηλοῖ διὰ τῶν ἐφεξῆς</foreign> to the end.</note>
