              </msItem>
              <msItem xml:id="b3" n="4">
                <locus to="5" from="4a">Foll. 4a-5</locus>
                
                <title xml:lang="en">On the Human Nature of <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/2245">our Lord</persName>.</title>
                <rubric xml:lang="syr">ܕܥܠ ܐܢܫܘܬܗ ܕܡܪܢ ܢܦܫ̈ܬܐ ܕܪ̈ܚܡܢ ܠܐܠܗܐ ܚܒ̈ܝܒܝ܆ ܟܠܝܘܡ
